autocmd FileType ruby nmap <buffer> <C-f> <Plug>(xmpfilter-mark)
autocmd FileType ruby xmap <buffer> <C-f> <Plug>(xmpfilter-mark)
autocmd FileType ruby imap <buffer> <C-f> <Plug>(xmpfilter-mark)

autocmd FileType ruby nmap <buffer> <C-g> <Plug>(xmpfilter-run)
autocmd FileType ruby xmap <buffer> <C-g> <Plug>(xmpfilter-run)
autocmd FileType ruby imap <buffer> <C-g> <Plug>(xmpfilter-run)
